-- 22-fact-checked-article-frames.cell (v0.2)
-- Execution trace of 22-fact-checked-article.cell via eval-one
--
-- v0.2 execution notes:
--   - File-scope ⊨? active: retry max 3 with failure context, then ⊥
--   - rewrite-article has guard: `where all-pass = false` (skipped when all pass)
--   - final-article has guard: `where all-pass = true` (fires only on success)
--   - incomplete-article has guard: `where all-pass = false` (fires only on failure)
--   - ⊢∘ fact-check-loop: custom label, blessed by v0.2 naming convention
--   - Oracles on generate-article (⊢∘ target) are aspirational under v0.2
--   - ⊢⊢ spawn-fact-checkers: replace mode — each iteration discards prior checkers
--   - Wildcard deps (fact-check-*→field) are v0.2 compliant
--   - aggregate-results is ⊢= (hard cell) — deterministic, no LLM
--
-- Meta: A fact-checked article pipeline. The ⊢∘ loop drives article
-- quality by spawning per-claim fact-checkers, aggregating verdicts,
-- and rewriting failures. Converges when all claims pass.

-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- READY-SET ANALYSIS (initial state)
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- Ready: { topic } — no givens, always ready (⊢= hard cell)
-- Blocked: { generate-article } — needs topic→title, topic→scope
-- Blocked: { spawn-fact-checkers } — needs generate-article→claims
-- Blocked: { aggregate-results } — needs fact-check-*→verdict (no fact-check cells exist)
-- Blocked: { rewrite-article } — needs aggregate-results→failed-claims + guard
-- Blocked: { final-article } — needs aggregate-results→all-pass + guard
-- Blocked: { incomplete-article } — needs aggregate-results→all-pass + guard
-- Not spawned: fact-check-template (template, not directly evaluated)

