-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- Ready set: { topic } — no givens, always ready
-- Blocked: all others (transitive)

⊢ topic
  yield title, scope

  ⊢= title ← "The History of Version Control Systems"
  ⊢= scope ← "From early mainframe source management through distributed version control. Cover SCCS, RCS, CVS, Subversion, BitKeeper, Git, and Mercurial. Focus on factual milestones: creation dates, creators, key technical innovations."

-- eval-one: topic is a hard cell (⊢=). Deterministic evaluation.
-- Both yields bound directly. No LLM needed.

  yield title ≡ "The History of Version Control Systems"
  yield scope ≡ "From early mainframe source management through distributed version control. Cover SCCS, RCS, CVS, Subversion, BitKeeper, Git, and Mercurial. Focus on factual milestones: creation dates, creators, key technical innovations."

-- No oracles on topic. Frozen immediately.

-- state after frame 0: topic frozen.
-- Ready set: { generate-article } — topic→title + topic→scope now available
-- ⊢∘ fact-check-loop begins: iteration 0

-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-- ⊢∘ FACT-CHECK-LOOP — ITERATION 0
-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
